{'en': {'shortDesc': 'Hardware Color Profiler', 'pkgName': 'lprof', 'longDesc': u'\n\nLPROF is a color profiler that creates ICC compliant profiles for devices such as cameras, scanners, and monitors. These profiles provide color consistency across devices. They can be used in color profile-aware software such as The Gimp and Scribus. For an example of creating a profile that can be used with Scribus see http://www.atlantictechsolutions.com/scribusdocs/lcms/moncal.html.'}}